         <a href="https://wiki.unrealengine.com/VaRest_Plugin" target="_blank">VaRest plugin</a> sending <abbr
           title="JavaScript Object Notation">JSON</abbr> data back and forth.</p>

        <p>Apart from the above, I've managed to build <span class="title">We Ride</span> entirely using Blueprint!</p>

