        <p>In <abbr title="player versus player">pvp</abbr>, speed is key, so make sure you've configured your hotkeys and equipped the best
         combination of armors and weapons you can muster!</p>
        <p>You can see the top six fighters, and the reward for killing them, in the Score section!</p>
